n&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:p|text_align:center&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;gtt_home_sectionOne&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Check visa requirements before traveling, ensuring a smooth entry and compliance with destination regulations.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; el_class=&#8221;gth_home_icon_box&#8221;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;30474&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1703793925702{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Health and Safety Tips&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:p|text_align:center&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;gtt_home_sectionOne&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Prioritize health, stay hydrated, follow safety guidelines, and maintain personal hygiene for a secure journey.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; el_class=&#8221;gth_home_icon_box&#8221;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;30475&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1703793937806{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Currency and Tipping&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:p|text_align:center&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;gtt_home_sectionOne&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Familiarize with local currency, consider customary tipping practices for respectful and seamless travel experiences.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;30px&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; el_class=&#8221;float-left cta-package&#8221; el_id=&#8221;cta_section_tour&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1683730393587{background-image: url(https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/tour-package-cta-ye